info.description: Manages OS login configuration for Google account users.
info.title: Cloud OS Login

parameters.description:
A reference to the POSIX account to update. POSIX accounts are identified
by the project ID they are associated with. A reference to the POSIX
account is in format `users/{user}/projects/{project}`.
parameters.name: name

parameters.description:
The fingerprint of the public key to retrieve. Public keys are identified
by their SHA-256 fingerprint. The fingerprint of the public key is in
format `users/{user}/sshPublicKeys/{fingerprint}`.
parameters.name: name

patch.description:
Updates an SSH public key and returns the profile information. This method
supports patch semantics.

parameters.description:
The fingerprint of the public key to update. Public keys are identified by
their SHA-256 fingerprint. The fingerprint of the public key is in format
`users/{user}/sshPublicKeys/{fingerprint}`.
parameters.name: name

parameters.description: Mask to control which fields get updated. Updates all if not present.
parameters.name: updateMask

get.description:
Retrieves the profile information used for logging in to a virtual machine
on Google Compute Engine.

parameters.name: name

parameters.description: The project ID of the Google Cloud Platform project.
parameters.name: projectId

parameters.description: A system ID for filtering the results of the request.
parameters.name: systemId

schema.description:
The user profile information used for logging in to a virtual machine on
Google Compute Engine.
